name: Peezy
description: Peezy, also known as Young Peezy, is the cool alter ego and social media persona of Pepe from Matt Furie’s Boy’s Club. Peezy is featured on pages 143 and 154 in the Boy's Club. Unlike Pepe’s more chill demeanor, Peezy embodies confidence and effortlessly commands attention. He doesn’t rely on trying to impress—his natural charisma and ability to shift the vibe make him stand out. Where Pepe might struggle to connect, Peezy shines, effortlessly becoming the center of attention and leaving a lasting impression.
